<HL>
   Obscure Law That Gives GIs a Break
   On Rates Stirs Concern Among Banks
   ----
   By Arthur S. Hayes
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/23/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
<IN>
